  <summary>5/12/2005--Introduced.
United States Seaport Multiyear Security Enhancement Act - Authorizes the Transportation Security Administration (TSA) to make grants to seaports to enhance security if the TSA determines that the grant will improve security at a seaport or improve the efficiency of the seaport without lessening security.</summary>
